<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About the Company - Prime Infra</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/publicapplicant.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Styles for layout and design */
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .announcements, .about-us {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        .announcements h2, .about-us h2, .values-heading {
            color: #07ACB9;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .announcement-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .announcement-item {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .announcement-item:hover {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
        }
        .announcement-item .subject {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .announcement-item .timestamp {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .announcement-item .description {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .announcement-item img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .no-announcement {
            text-align: center;
            color: #999;
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/publicheader') %>

    <!-- Announcements Section -->
    <section class="announcements">
        <h2>ANNOUNCEMENTS</h2>
        <div class="announcement-content">
            <% if (announcements && announcements.length > 0) { %>
                <% announcements.forEach(announcement => { %>
                    <div class="announcement-item">
                        <div class="subject"><%= announcement.subject %></div>
                        <div class="timestamp">Posted on: <%= new Date(announcement.created_at).toLocaleDateString() %></div>
                        <div class="description"><%= announcement.content %></div>
                        <% if (announcement.imageUrl) { %>
                            <img src="<%= announcement.imageUrl %>" alt="Announcement Image">
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <p class="no-announcement">No announcements available at the moment.</p>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section class="about-us">
        <div class="purpose-mission">
            <div class="purpose">
                <h2>PURPOSE</h2>
                <p>Better lives and resilient economies through critical infrastructure.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mission">
                <h2>MISSION</h2>
                <p>Transforming developing markets around the world by providing them with reliable, resilient, and sustainable infrastructure, carried out through fast and lean management processes, a holistic thinking approach, and a customer-centric mindset.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="values-heading">OUR VALUES</h2>
        <div class="values-container">
            <div class="value">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-star"></i> VALUE CREATION</h3>
                <p>We create meaningful value by investing in projects that improve the quality of life for our host communities, investing in the development and welfare of our employees, and managing these investments to deliver high returns to our shareholders.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> INTEGRITY</h3>
                <p>We are ethical, fair, and transparent in our business practices at every level of our organization while delivering a profitable and sustainable business, and expect similar behavior from our business partners.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> PIONEERING</h3>
                <p>We evolve new approaches, explore new methods and ideas, in order to create innovative solutions and deliver lasting impact for the countries in which we operate.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> PASSION</h3>
                <p>We live and breathe the work that we do, and seek out colleagues and business partners that share the same deep commitment to our purpose.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
